On Tue, 4 Jan 2005, Brian Gerst wrote:
> > +#define pud_test_and_populate(mm, pud, pmd) \
> > +		(cmpxchg((int *)pgd, PUD_NONE, _PAGE_TABLE | __pa(pmd)) == PUD_NONE)
>                                  ^^^
> Shouldn't this be pud?
Corrrect. Sigh. Could someone test this on x86_64?
